tales-tumbler: tales-tumbler (thumbnail generator)
tales-tumbler:
tales-tumbler: Tumbler is a D-Bus service for applications to request thumbnails
tales-tumbler: for various URI schemes and MIME types. It is written in an object-
tales-tumbler: oriented fashion using GLib and GObject. It provides plugin
tales-tumbler: interfaces for extending the URI schemes and MIME types for which
tales-tumbler: thumbnails can be generated as well as for replacing the storage
tales-tumbler: backend that is used to store the thumbnails on disk. 
tales-tumbler:
